Package org.fluidity.deployment.plugin.spi

Service provider interfaces for the standalone JAR/WAR/OSGi application Maven plugins.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JarManifest
    JAR manifest transformation for application wrappers.
    JarManifest.Dependencies
    Handles the dependencies of the host project.
    SecurityPolicy
    Manage a security policy file.
    SecurityPolicy.Output
    Something where a named entry can be saved.
    ServerBootstrap
    Bootstraps an HTTP server and deploys one or more WAR files.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    JarManifest.Packaging
    Maven profile names for the implementation project to declare dependencies not to include, to include, or to unpack, respectively, in the project artifact being processed.
